            "default": "Studio Noir operates from a 280 sqm daylight studio in DIFC, and travels freely — I've shot in 47 countries and returned to most of them for second jobs. If you're here, you're probably the kind of person who cares about how things will feel to look at in twenty years. Let's make something worth keeping."
